"title": "4476: meals",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4476: meals",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Food eaten at set times, on special occasions or following significant events. Sacrificial meals formed part of Israelite worship in the OT, as does the Lord's Supper for worship by believers in the NT.</p>\n<h2>Regular daily meals</h2>\n<h2>Breakfast</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:12\">JHN 21:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Lunch</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:12-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:12–14:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:16\">GEN 43:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:31-Gen43:34\">GEN 43:31–43:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:14\">RUT 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:9-Acts10:10\">ACT 10:9–10:10</a></p>\n<h3>Evening meal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:7-Luke17:8\">LUK 17:7–17:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:10-Matt9:13\">MAT 9:10–9:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:15-Mark2:17\">MRK 2:15–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:29-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:29–5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:3\">MRK 14:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36\">LUK 7:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:1-John12:2\">JHN 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:12-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:12–14:14</a></p>\n<h2>Royal meals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:20\">GEN 40:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:18-1Sam20:34\">1SA 20:18–20:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:9-2Sam9:13\">2SA 9:9–9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:22-1Kgs4:28\">1KI 4:22–4:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:19\">1KI 18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:1-Esth1:12\">EST 1:1–1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:18\">EST 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth7:1-Esth7:10\">EST 7:1–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:6-Matt14:11\">MAT 14:6–14:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:21-Mark6:28\">MRK 6:21–6:28</a></p>\n<h2>Meals of the poor</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:17\">PRO 15:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:10-1Kgs17:16\">1KI 17:10–17:16</a></p>\n<h2>Sacrificial meals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:53-Gen31:54\">GEN 31:53–31:54</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:1-Exod12:11\">EXO 12:1–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:31-Exod29:34\">EXO 29:31–29:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:14-Lev6:29\">LEV 6:14–6:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev7:1-Lev7:6\">LEV 7:1–7:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev8:31\">LEV 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:12-Lev10:15\">LEV 10:12–10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:1-Deut16:8\">DEU 16:1–16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:3-1Sam1:8\">1SA 1:3–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:11-1Sam9:24\">1SA 9:11–9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:28-1Sam20:29\">1SA 20:28–20:29</a></p>\n<h2>Symbolic meals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:20-Matt26:29\">MAT 26:20–26:29</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:17-Mark14:25\">MRK 14:17–14:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:14-Luke22:22\">LUK 22:14–22:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:17-1Cor11:34\">1CO 11:17–11:34</a></p>\n<h2>Wedding and funeral meals</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:1-Matt22:14\">MAT 22:1–22:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:16-Luke14:24\">LUK 14:16–14:24</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:5\">JER 16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:1-John2:10\">JHN 2:1–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:6-Rev19:9\">REV 19:6–19:9</a></p>\n<h2>Meals and hospitality</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:8\">2KI 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:1-Gen18:8\">GEN 18:1–18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:1-Gen19:3\">GEN 19:1–19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:24-Judg5:25\">JDG 5:24–5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:15-Judg13:16\">JDG 13:15–13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:24-1Sam28:25\">1SA 28:24–28:25</a></p>\n<h2>Meals as occasions of fellowship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:20\">REV 3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:17\">PRO 15:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:29-Luke5:32\">LUK 5:29–5:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36\">LUK 7:36</a></p>",
